text: Boeotus of Sicyon was an ancient Greek athlete listed by Eusebius of Caesarea as a victor in the stadion race of the 164th Olympiad (124 BC).Eusebius of Caesarea, Chronicle . == References == == See also == Olympic winners of the Stadion race Category:Ancient Olympic competitors Category:Ancient Achaean athletes Category:2nd-century BC Greek people Category:Ancient Sicyonians Category:Sicyon
title: Boeotus of Sicyon
